Find the number of solutions in non-negative reals to the following system of equations:
\[
\begin{cases}
x_1 + x_n^2 = 4x_n \\
x_2 + x_1^2 = 4x_1 \\
\vdots \\
x_n + x_{n-1}^2 = 4x_{n-1}
\end{cases}
\]

